# Running Tests in the Swirl Project
------------------------------------

This README provides instructions on how to run tests for the Swirl project.

## Installation
---------------

Before running the tests, ensure that all test dependencies are installed.
To install the required dependencies, execute the following command in your
terminal:

pip install -r requirements-test.txt


## Running Pre-Checkin Tests
----------------------------

It's recommended to run the pre-checkin tests before submitting a pull request.

Execute the pre-checkin test script with the following command:

./DevUtils/pre-checkin-tests.sh


## Additional API tests
-----------------------

To run addiational API tests, execute the test script:

./DevUtils/run-integtration-tests.sh
